org.cpsolver.studentsct.model

Class Course

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.assignment.context.AbstractClassWithContext<Request,Enrollment,Course.CourseContext>
      • org.cpsolver.studentsct.model.Course
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CanHoldContext, CanInheritContext<Request,Enrollment,Course.CourseContext>, HasAssignmentContext<Request,Enrollment,Course.CourseContext>

    public class Course
extends AbstractClassWithContext<Request,Enrollment,Course.CourseContext>
implements CanInheritContext<Request,Enrollment,Course.CourseContext>
    Representation of a course offering. A course offering contains id, subject area, course number and an instructional offering.

    Each instructional offering (see Offering) is offered under one or more course offerings.

    Version:
